<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I would not recommend this book to readers younger than 16. Even then it would depend on the kid.... It tackles mature subjects (sex and sexuality, vi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I would not recommend this book to readers younger than 16. Even then it would depend on the kid.... It tackles mature subjects (sex and sexuality, violence, abandonment, lots of death) and is not a "straightforward" book; it needs a sophisticated reader. Some knowledge of Spanish also helps.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
