      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780452272095" href="/book/show/1290994.So_Far_from_God">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/205963-lindsay?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/205963-lindsay?shelf=lgbtq">lgbtq</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/205963-lindsay?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/205963-lindsay?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
