          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer112711829" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14225895898470651985">I loved this book so much I found myself literally hugging it. I neglected so many other things just to sit down and take time reveling in it. Dreamy books like this are my favorite--I loved how timeless it felt even when it was very much of its time. I will return to this one, again and again.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


